\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\left[\boldsymbol{\omega}\times\right]=\left[\begin{array}{ccc}
0 & -\omega_{z} & \omega_{y}\\
\omega_{z} & 0 & -\omega_{x}\\
-\omega_{y} & \omega_{x} & 0
\end{array}\right]
\]

\end_inset

这个斜对称矩阵
\begin_inset Formula $\left[\boldsymbol{\omega}\times\right]$
