\begin_inset Formula $\boldsymbol{R}\left(\boldsymbol{\omega},\theta\right)=e^{\left[\boldsymbol{\omega}\times\right]\theta}=\boldsymbol{I}+\left[\boldsymbol{\omega}\times\right]\sin\left(\theta\right)+\left[\boldsymbol{\omega}\times\right]^{2}\left(1-\cos\left(\theta\right)\right)$
\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
